Class PlayerInfoData

java.lang.Object
com.comphenix.protocol.wrappers.PlayerInfoData
public class PlayerInfoData extends Object
Represents an immutable PlayerInfoData in the PLAYER_INFO packet.

      Constructs a new PlayerInfoData for Minecraft 1.19 or later without signature data
      Parameters:
      profileId - the id of the profile (has to be non-null)
      latency - the latency in milliseconds
      listed - whether the player is listed in the tab list
      gameMode - the game mode
      profile - the game profile
      displayName - display name in tab list (optional)
